'''HD 102117b'''是一颗位于[[半人马座|半人马座]]、距离地球约137光年的系外行星，其母星为[[HD_102117|HD 102117]]。该行星是一颗小型[[类木行星|类木行星]]，其大小仅为木星的1/5。其轨道十分接近其母星，但还未如著名的[[飞马座51b|飞马座51b]]一般进入“烈焰轨道”(torch orbit)。该行星是迄今为止发现的最小的系外行星之一。<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/0004-637X/646/1/505/64046.html | author=Butler ''et al.'' | title=Catalog of Nearby Exoplanets | journal=The [[Astrophysical_Journal|Astrophysical Journal]] | volume=646 | issue=1 | pages=505–522 | year=2006 | doi=10.1086/504701 | access-date=2009-07-12 | archive-date=2009-05-02 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5gTrfcenD?url=http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/0004-637X/646/1/505/64046.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2004年，英澳行星搜索计划项目宣布在HD 102117附近发现了这颗行星。<ref name=""Anglo">{{cite journal | url=http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/0004-637X/623/2/1171/61345.html | author=Tinney ''et al.'' | title=Three Low-Mass Planets from the Anglo-Australian Planet Search | journal=The [[Astrophysical_Journal|Astrophysical Journal]] | volume=623 | issue=2 | year=2005 | pages=1171–1179  | doi=10.1086/428661 }}</ref>不久之后[[高精度径向速度行星搜索器|高精度径向速度行星搜索器]]项目小组也宣布证实了这颗行星的存在。两支团队均是使用视向速度法探测到这颗行星的。<ref name="HARPS">{{cite journal | url=http://www.edpsciences.org/articles/aa/abs/2005/27/aa2864-05/aa2864-05.html | author=Lovis ''et al.'' | title=The HARPS search for southern extra-solar planets III. Three Saturn-mass planets around HD 93083, HD 101930 and HD 102117 | journal=[[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] | volume=437 | year=2005 | pages=1121 – 1126 | doi=10.1051/0004-6361:20052864 | format=abstract | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20051023053345/http://www.edpsciences.org/articles/aa/abs/2005/27/aa2864-05/aa2864-05.html | archivedate=2005-10-23 | access-date=2009-07-12 }}</ref>

